<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/andrew-champ> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Andrew Champ has 30 years of international major project development and delivery experience including successful delivery of Barakah Nuclear Power plant in the UAE. Having worked in the supply chain and as a Client Andrew is a big advocate for sustainable procurement and building collaborative relationships. Andrew is now the Commercial Director for RWM and sits on the GDF Programme Board building the Intelligent Client capability with a view of becoming an ‘athletic client’ working with strategic partners to deliver the UK’s biggest environmental National Significant Infrastructure Project, which is the GDF."@en .
